{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":940,"text":"Sadly,"},{"time":2940,"text":"in the next 18 minutes when I do our chat,"},{"time":6227,"text":"four Americans that are alive"},{"time":8940,"text":"will be dead through\nthe food that they eat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14631,"text":"My name's Jamie Oliver."},{"time":16030,"text":"I'm 34 years old."},{"time":17781,"text":"I'm from Essex in England"},{"time":19940,"text":"and for the last seven years"},{"time":22940,"text":"I've worked fairly tirelessly\nto save lives in my own way."},{"time":29124,"text":"I'm not a doctor;"},{"time":30940,"text":"I'm a chef,"},{"time":32141,"text":"I don't have expensive equipment"},{"time":34687,"text":"or medicine."},{"time":35781,"text":"I use information, education."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39265,"text":"I profoundly believe\nthat the power of food"},{"time":42266,"text":"has a primal place in our homes"},{"time":45465,"text":"that binds us to the best bits of life."},{"time":51860,"text":"We have an awful, awful reality right now."},{"time":58519,"text":"America, you're at the top of your game."},{"time":61940,"text":"This is one of the most unhealthy\ncountries in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65630,"text":"Can I please just see a raise of hands"},{"time":68300,"text":"for how many of you have\nchildren in this room today?"},{"time":70903,"text":"Put your hands up."},{"time":72328,"text":"You can continue to put your hands up,\naunties and uncles as well."},{"time":76272,"text":"Most of you. OK."},{"time":78273,"text":"We, the adults of the last\nfour generations,"},{"time":81274,"text":"have blessed our children with the destiny"},{"time":84163,"text":"of a shorter lifespan\nthan their own parents."},{"time":90019,"text":"Your child will live a life\nten years younger than you"},{"time":94940,"text":"because of the landscape of food\nthat we've built around them."},{"time":99335,"text":"Two-thirds of this room,"},{"time":100844,"text":"today, in America, are statistically\noverweight or obese."},{"time":104174,"text":"You lot, you're all right,"},{"time":105445,"text":"but we'll get you eventually, don't worry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107484,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":108940,"text":"The statistics of bad health are clear,"},{"time":111940,"text":"very clear."},{"time":113749,"text":"We spend our lives being paranoid\nabout death, murder, homicide,"},{"time":117397,"text":"you name it; it's on the front page\nof every paper, CNN."},{"time":120940,"text":"Look at homicide\nat the bottom, for God's sake."},{"time":124338,"text":"Right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":125393,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":126940,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":131940,"text":"Every single one of those in the red\nis a diet-related disease."},{"time":136280,"text":"Any doctor, any specialist\nwill tell you that."},{"time":138892,"text":"Fact: diet-related disease\nis the biggest killer"},{"time":142203,"text":"in the United States,\nright now, here today."},{"time":148045,"text":"This is a global problem."},{"time":150510,"text":"It's a catastrophe."},{"time":151686,"text":"It's sweeping the world."},{"time":153178,"text":"England is right behind you, as usual."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156153,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160384,"text":"I know they were close,\nbut not that close."},{"time":163106,"text":"We need a revolution."},{"time":164478,"text":"Mexico, Australia, Germany,"},{"time":166781,"text":"India, China,"},{"time":168033,"text":"all have massive problems\nof obesity and bad health."},{"time":172725,"text":"Think about smoking."},{"time":175034,"text":"It costs way less than obesity now."},{"time":177677,"text":"Obesity costs you Americans\n10 percent of your health-care bills,"},{"time":182611,"text":"150 billion dollars a year."},{"time":187014,"text":"In 10 years, it's set to double:"},{"time":188940,"text":"300 billion dollars a year."},{"time":190457,"text":"Let's be honest, guys,\nyou haven't got that cash."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192857,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":196765,"text":"I came here to start a food revolution\nthat I so profoundly believe in."},{"time":203180,"text":"We need it. The time is now."},{"time":205459,"text":"We're in a tipping-point moment."},{"time":207210,"text":"I've been doing this for seven years."},{"time":209019,"text":"I've been trying in America\nfor seven years."},{"time":211206,"text":"Now is the time when it's ripe --\nripe for the picking."},{"time":215114,"text":"I went to the eye of the storm."},{"time":216940,"text":"I went to West Virginia,\nthe most unhealthy state in America."},{"time":219893,"text":"Or it was last year."},{"time":220956,"text":"We've got a new one this year,\nbut we'll work on that next season."}]},{"cues":[{"time":224219,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226126,"text":"Huntington, West Virginia. Beautiful town."},{"time":228173,"text":"I wanted to put heart and soul and people,"},{"time":231694,"text":"your public,"},{"time":233473,"text":"around the statistics\nthat we've become so used to."},{"time":237344,"text":"I want to introduce you\nto some of the people that I care about:"},{"time":240368,"text":"your public, your children."},{"time":242012,"text":"I want to show a picture\nof my friend Brittany."},{"time":244585,"text":"She's 16 years old."},{"time":246868,"text":"She's got six years to live"},{"time":250382,"text":"because of the food that she's eaten."},{"time":253224,"text":"She's the third generation of Americans"},{"time":255352,"text":"that hasn't grown up\nwithin a food environment"},{"time":257567,"text":"where they've been taught\nto cook at home or in school,"},{"time":260180,"text":"or her mom, or her mom's mom."},{"time":262211,"text":"She has six years to live."},{"time":265527,"text":"She's eating her liver to death."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268400,"text":"Stacy, the Edwards family."},{"time":270353,"text":"This is a normal family, guys."},{"time":272940,"text":"Stacy does her best,\nbut she's third-generation as well;"},{"time":275790,"text":"she was never taught to cook\nat home or at school."},{"time":278163,"text":"The family's obese."},{"time":279322,"text":"Justin here, 12 years old,\nhe's 350 pounds."},{"time":282067,"text":"He gets bullied, for God's sake."},{"time":283759,"text":"The daughter there, Katie,\nshe's four years old."},{"time":286250,"text":"She's obese before she even gets\nto primary school."},{"time":289274,"text":"Marissa, she's all right,\nshe's one of your lot."},{"time":292222,"text":"But you know what?"},{"time":293269,"text":"Her father, who was obese,\ndied in her arms,"},{"time":296651,"text":"And then the second\nmost important man in her life,"},{"time":299079,"text":"her uncle, died of obesity,"},{"time":301627,"text":"and now her step-dad is obese."},{"time":304717,"text":"You see, the thing is,"},{"time":306517,"text":"obesity and diet-related disease"},{"time":308940,"text":"doesn't just hurt the people that have it;"},{"time":310964,"text":"it's all of their friends, families,\nbrothers, sisters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315153,"text":"Pastor Steve:"},{"time":316940,"text":"an inspirational man,"},{"time":318401,"text":"one of my early allies\nin Huntington, West Virginia."},{"time":321271,"text":"He's at the sharp knife-edge\nof this problem."},{"time":325215,"text":"He has to bury the people, OK?"},{"time":327572,"text":"And he's fed up with it."},{"time":328776,"text":"He's fed up with burying his friends,\nhis family, his community."},{"time":332127,"text":"Come winter, three times\nas many people die."},{"time":335456,"text":"He's sick of it."},{"time":336940,"text":"This is preventable disease.\nWaste of life."},{"time":339940,"text":"By the way, this is\nwhat they get buried in."},{"time":343265,"text":"We're not geared up to do this."},{"time":346043,"text":"Can't even get them out the door,\nand I'm being serious."},{"time":348695,"text":"Can't even get them there. Forklift."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351472,"text":"OK, I see it as a triangle, OK?"},{"time":353588,"text":"This is our landscape of food."},{"time":355144,"text":"I need you to understand it."},{"time":356525,"text":"You've probably heard all this before."},{"time":358613,"text":"Over the last 30 years,"},{"time":359923,"text":"what's happened that's ripped\nthe heart out of this country?"},{"time":362780,"text":"Let's be frank and honest."},{"time":365464,"text":"Well, modern-day life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367688,"text":"Let's start with the Main Street."},{"time":370067,"text":"Fast food has taken over\nthe whole country; we know that."},{"time":372775,"text":"The big brands are\nsome of the most important powers,"},{"time":375603,"text":"powerful powers, in this country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378053,"text":"(Sighs)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":379078,"text":"Supermarkets as well."},{"time":380820,"text":"Big companies. Big companies."},{"time":383211,"text":"Thirty years ago, most of the food"},{"time":386195,"text":"was largely local and largely fresh."},{"time":388940,"text":"Now it's largely processed\nand full of all sorts of additives,"},{"time":392323,"text":"extra ingredients,\nand you know the rest of the story."},{"time":395038,"text":"Portion size is obviously\na massive, massive problem."},{"time":399617,"text":"Labeling is a massive problem."},{"time":402273,"text":"The labeling in this country\nis a disgrace."},{"time":405430,"text":"The industry wants\nto self-police themselves."},{"time":410940,"text":"What, in this kind of climate?\nThey don't deserve it."},{"time":413519,"text":"How can you say something is low-fat\nwhen it's full of so much sugar?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":418011,"text":"Home."},{"time":421213,"text":"The biggest problem with the home"},{"time":422812,"text":"is that used to be the heart\nof passing on food culture,"},{"time":427940,"text":"what made our society."},{"time":430388,"text":"That is not happening anymore."},{"time":431845,"text":"And you know, as we go\nto work and as life changes,"},{"time":434750,"text":"and as life always evolves,"},{"time":436751,"text":"we kind of have\nto look at it holistically --"},{"time":438888,"text":"step back for a moment,\nand re-address the balance."},{"time":441300,"text":"It hasn't happened for 30 years, OK?"},{"time":444344,"text":"I want to show you a situation"},{"time":447726,"text":"that is very normal right now;\nthe Edwards family."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451582,"text":"(Video) Jamie Oliver: Let's have a talk."},{"time":454412,"text":"This stuff goes through you\nand your family's body every week."},{"time":458469,"text":"And I need you to know"},{"time":460402,"text":"that this is going to kill\nyour children early."},{"time":464550,"text":"How are you feeling?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":466639,"text":"Stacy: Just feeling really sad\nand depressed right now."},{"time":470630,"text":"But, you know, I want\nmy kids to succeed in life"},{"time":473767,"text":"and this isn't going to get them there."},{"time":476749,"text":"But I'm killing them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479655,"text":"JO: Yes you are. You are."},{"time":482655,"text":"But we can stop that."},{"time":487757,"text":"Normal."},{"time":490006,"text":"Let's get on schools,"},{"time":491864,"text":"something that I'm fairly much\na specialist in."},{"time":494940,"text":"OK, school."},{"time":496940,"text":"What is school? Who invented it?\nWhat's the purpose of school?"},{"time":499940,"text":"School was always invented\nto arm us with the tools"},{"time":502796,"text":"to make us creative, do wonderful things,"},{"time":505639,"text":"make us earn a living, etc., etc."},{"time":508120,"text":"You know, it's been kind of in this sort\nof tight box for a long, long time, OK?"},{"time":512940,"text":"But we haven't really evolved it"},{"time":514940,"text":"to deal with the health\ncatastrophes of America, OK?"},{"time":518294,"text":"School food is something"},{"time":521405,"text":"that most kids --\n31 million a day, actually --"},{"time":524087,"text":"have twice a day, more than often,\nbreakfast and lunch,"},{"time":528772,"text":"180 days of the year."},{"time":530525,"text":"So you could say that school\nfood is quite important, really,"},{"time":533724,"text":"judging the circumstances."}]},{"cues":[{"time":535334,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":540399,"text":"Before I crack into my rant,"},{"time":542940,"text":"which I'm sure you're waiting for --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544990,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":548061,"text":"I need to say one thing,\nand it's so important"},{"time":550451,"text":"in, hopefully, the magic\nthat happens and unfolds"},{"time":553182,"text":"in the next three months."},{"time":554940,"text":"The lunch ladies,\nthe lunch cooks of America --"},{"time":558253,"text":"I offer myself as their ambassador."},{"time":561652,"text":"I'm not slagging them off."},{"time":563162,"text":"They're doing the best they can do."},{"time":567828,"text":"They're doing their best."},{"time":569940,"text":"But they're doing what they're told,"},{"time":571796,"text":"and what they're being\ntold to do is wrong."},{"time":574376,"text":"The system is highly run by accountants;"},{"time":577637,"text":"there's not enough, or any,\nfood-knowledgeable people in the business."},{"time":581738,"text":"There's a problem:"},{"time":582793,"text":"If you're not a food expert,\nand you've got tight budgets"},{"time":585940,"text":"and it's getting tighter,\nthen you can't be creative,"},{"time":588674,"text":"you can't duck and dive\nand write different things around things."},{"time":591837,"text":"If you're an accountant, and a box-ticker,"},{"time":593868,"text":"the only thing you can do\nin these circumstances"},{"time":596138,"text":"is buy cheaper shit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597190,"text":"Now, the reality is,"},{"time":598544,"text":"the food that your kids get\nevery day is fast food,"},{"time":602179,"text":"it's highly processed,"},{"time":603512,"text":"there's not enough\nfresh food in there at all."},{"time":605776,"text":"You know, the amount\nof additives, E numbers,"},{"time":607981,"text":"ingredients you wouldn't believe --"},{"time":609711,"text":"there's not enough veggies at all."},{"time":611446,"text":"French fries are considered a vegetable."},{"time":613394,"text":"Pizza for breakfast.\nThey don't even get crockery."},{"time":615940,"text":"Knives and forks?\nNo, they're too dangerous."},{"time":619097,"text":"They have scissors in the classroom,"},{"time":620861,"text":"but knives and forks? No."},{"time":622266,"text":"And the way I look at it is:"},{"time":623686,"text":"If you don't have knives\nand forks in your school,"},{"time":626099,"text":"you're purely endorsing,"},{"time":627662,"text":"from a state level, fast food,\nbecause it's handheld."},{"time":630758,"text":"And yes, by the way, it is fast food:"},{"time":632567,"text":"It's sloppy Joes, it's burgers,"},{"time":634181,"text":"it's wieners, it's pizzas,\nit's all of that stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":638205,"text":"(Sighs)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":640392,"text":"Ten percent of what we spend\non health care, as I said earlier,"},{"time":643393,"text":"is on obesity, and it's going to double."},{"time":647090,"text":"We're not teaching our kids."},{"time":648544,"text":"There's no statutory right\nto teach kids about food,"},{"time":651273,"text":"elementary or secondary school, OK?"},{"time":653090,"text":"We don't teach kids about food, right?"},{"time":655432,"text":"And this is a little clip\nfrom an elementary school,"},{"time":657885,"text":"which is very common in England."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661940,"text":"(Video) Who knows what this is?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":663493,"text":"Child: Potatoes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664588,"text":"Jamie Oliver: Potato?\nSo, you think these are potatoes?"},{"time":667200,"text":"Do you know what that is?"},{"time":668734,"text":"Do you know what that is?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":669962,"text":"Child: Broccoli?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":671001,"text":"JO: What about this? Our good old friend."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673481,"text":"Child: Celery."}]},{"cues":[{"time":674665,"text":"JO: No. What do you think this is?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":676633,"text":"Child: Onion.\nJO: Onion? No."}]},{"cues":[{"time":678141,"text":"JO: Immediately you\nget a really clear sense"},{"time":680571,"text":"of \"Do the kids know anything\nabout where food comes from?\""},{"time":683815,"text":"Who knows what that is? Child: Uh, pear?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":685816,"text":"JO: What do you think this is?\nChild: I don't know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":688268,"text":"JO: If the kids don't know what stuff is,"},{"time":690276,"text":"then they will never eat it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693863,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":695144,"text":"JO: Normal. England and America,"},{"time":697940,"text":"England and America."},{"time":699502,"text":"Guess what fixed that."},{"time":702107,"text":"Two one-hour sessions."},{"time":705151,"text":"We've got to start teaching our kids\nabout food in schools, period."}]},{"cues":[{"time":709376,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":714940,"text":"I want to tell you about something"},{"time":718985,"text":"that kind of epitomizes the trouble\nthat we're in, guys, OK?"},{"time":723347,"text":"I want to talk about something\nso basic as milk."},{"time":726582,"text":"Every kid has the right to milk at school."},{"time":728607,"text":"Your kids will be having milk\nat school, breakfast and lunch, right?"},{"time":732227,"text":"They'll be having two bottles, OK?"},{"time":734049,"text":"And most kids do."},{"time":735566,"text":"But milk ain't good enough anymore."},{"time":738375,"text":"Don't get me wrong, I support milk --"},{"time":740940,"text":"but someone at the milk board"},{"time":743080,"text":"probably paid a lot of money\nfor some geezer to work out"},{"time":745774,"text":"that if you put loads of flavorings,"},{"time":747539,"text":"colorings and sugar in milk,"},{"time":748986,"text":"more kids will drink it."},{"time":751645,"text":"Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":753161,"text":"Obviously now that's going to catch on"},{"time":755138,"text":"the apple board is going to work out"},{"time":756948,"text":"that if they make toffee apples\nthey'll eat more as well."},{"time":759749,"text":"Do you know what I mean?"},{"time":761186,"text":"For me, there isn't any need\nto flavor the milk."},{"time":764257,"text":"Okay? There's sugar in everything."},{"time":766304,"text":"I know the ins and outs\nof those ingredients."},{"time":768477,"text":"It's in everything."},{"time":769527,"text":"Even the milk hasn't escaped\nthe kind of modern-day problems."},{"time":773129,"text":"There's our milk. There's our carton."},{"time":774940,"text":"In that is nearly as much sugar\nas one of your favorite cans of fizzy pop,"},{"time":779213,"text":"and they are having two a day."},{"time":780673,"text":"So, let me just show you."},{"time":782252,"text":"We've got one kid, here --"},{"time":787027,"text":"having, you know,\neight tablespoons of sugar a day."},{"time":791559,"text":"You know, there's your week."},{"time":794440,"text":"There's your month."},{"time":797518,"text":"And I've taken the liberty of putting in"},{"time":799737,"text":"just the five years\nof elementary school sugar,"},{"time":806393,"text":"just from milk."},{"time":810940,"text":"Now, I don't know about you guys,"},{"time":812784,"text":"but judging the circumstances, right,"},{"time":815625,"text":"any judge in the whole world,"},{"time":817940,"text":"would look at the statistics\nand the evidence,"},{"time":820428,"text":"and they would find any government\nof old guilty of child abuse."},{"time":824268,"text":"That's my belief."}]},{"cues":[{"time":825396,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":832287,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":833940,"text":"Now, if I came up here, and I wish\nI could come up here today"},{"time":837256,"text":"and hang a cure for AIDS or cancer,"},{"time":839941,"text":"you'd be fighting\nand scrambling to get to me."},{"time":843424,"text":"This, all this bad news, is preventable."},{"time":846940,"text":"That's the good news."},{"time":848475,"text":"It's very, very preventable."},{"time":851220,"text":"So, let's just think about,\nwe got a problem here,"},{"time":853940,"text":"we need to reboot."},{"time":856273,"text":"Okay so, in my world,\nwhat do we need to do?"},{"time":858940,"text":"Here is the thing, right,"},{"time":860679,"text":"it cannot just come from one source."},{"time":862940,"text":"To reboot and make real tangible change,"},{"time":866371,"text":"real change, so that I could look you\nin the white of the eyes"},{"time":869339,"text":"and say, \"In 10 years' time,"},{"time":870940,"text":"the history of your children's lives,"},{"time":872940,"text":"happiness -- and let's not forget,\nyou're clever if you eat well,"},{"time":876012,"text":"you know you're going to live longer --"},{"time":877894,"text":"all of that stuff,\nit will look different. OK?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":881546,"text":"So, supermarkets."},{"time":883276,"text":"Where else do you shop so religiously?"},{"time":885220,"text":"Week in, week out."},{"time":886432,"text":"How much money do you spend,\nin your life, in a supermarket?"},{"time":889535,"text":"Love them."},{"time":890567,"text":"They just sell us what we want. All right."},{"time":892647,"text":"They owe us to put a food ambassador\nin every major supermarket."},{"time":897622,"text":"They need to help us shop."},{"time":899226,"text":"They need to show us how to cook\nquick, tasty, seasonal meals"},{"time":902940,"text":"for people that are busy."},{"time":904829,"text":"This is not expensive."},{"time":906822,"text":"It is done in some, and it needs\nto be done across the board"},{"time":909727,"text":"in America soon, and quick."},{"time":911804,"text":"The big brands, you know, the food brands,"},{"time":914805,"text":"need to put food education\nat the heart of their businesses."},{"time":918554,"text":"I know, easier said than done."},{"time":920458,"text":"It's the future. It's the only way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":922693,"text":"Fast food."},{"time":924338,"text":"With the fast-food industry"},{"time":927122,"text":"you know, it's very competitive."},{"time":928940,"text":"I've had loads\nof secret papers and dealings"},{"time":931059,"text":"with fast food restaurants."},{"time":932801,"text":"I know how they do it."},{"time":934642,"text":"I mean, basically they've weaned us on"},{"time":936939,"text":"to these hits of sugar,\nsalt and fat, and x, y, and z,"},{"time":939742,"text":"and everyone loves them, right?"},{"time":941743,"text":"So, these guys are going\nto be part of the solution."},{"time":944963,"text":"But we need to get the government to work"},{"time":946940,"text":"with all of the fast food purveyors\nand the restaurant industry,"},{"time":950012,"text":"and over a five, six, seven year period"},{"time":952085,"text":"wean of us off the extreme amounts"},{"time":954428,"text":"of fat, sugar and all the other\nnon-food ingredients."}]},{"cues":[{"time":957940,"text":"Now, also, back to the sort of big brands:"},{"time":960246,"text":"labeling, I said earlier,\nis an absolute farce"},{"time":963452,"text":"and has got to be sorted."},{"time":966243,"text":"OK, school."},{"time":968470,"text":"Obviously, in schools, we owe it to them"},{"time":970940,"text":"to make sure those 180 days of the year,"},{"time":972940,"text":"from that little precious age of four,"},{"time":974940,"text":"until 18, 20, 24, whatever,"},{"time":976940,"text":"they need to be cooked proper, fresh food"},{"time":981815,"text":"from local growers on site, OK?"},{"time":983940,"text":"There needs to be a new\nstandard of fresh, proper food"},{"time":986490,"text":"for your children, yeah?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":987940,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":992393,"text":"Under the circumstances,\nit's profoundly important"},{"time":995853,"text":"that every single\nAmerican child leaves school"},{"time":998446,"text":"knowing how to cook 10 recipes"},{"time":1000447,"text":"that will save their life."},{"time":1002940,"text":"Life skills."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1004043,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1006264,"text":"That means that they can be\nstudents, young parents,"},{"time":1009326,"text":"and be able to sort of duck and dive\naround the basics of cooking,"},{"time":1013589,"text":"no matter what recession hits\nthem next time."},{"time":1015716,"text":"If you can cook,\nrecession money doesn't matter."},{"time":1018122,"text":"If you can cook, time doesn't matter."},{"time":1022135,"text":"The workplace, we haven't\nreally talked about it."},{"time":1024604,"text":"You know, it's now time\nfor corporate responsibility"},{"time":1028190,"text":"to really look at what they feed\nor make available to their staff."},{"time":1032238,"text":"The staff are the moms and dads\nof America's children."},{"time":1035572,"text":"Marissa, her father died in her hand,"},{"time":1037755,"text":"I think she'd be quite happy"},{"time":1039756,"text":"if corporate America could start\nfeeding their staff properly."},{"time":1042940,"text":"Definitely they shouldn't be left out."},{"time":1044940,"text":"Let's go back to the home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1046530,"text":"Now, look, if we do\nall this stuff, and we can,"},{"time":1048794,"text":"it's so achievable."},{"time":1049891,"text":"You can care and be commercial."},{"time":1051657,"text":"Absolutely."},{"time":1052704,"text":"But the home needs to start passing on\ncooking again, for sure."},{"time":1057723,"text":"For sure, pass it on as a philosophy."},{"time":1060213,"text":"And for me, it's quite romantic,"},{"time":1061881,"text":"but it's about if one person\nteaches three people"},{"time":1064298,"text":"how to cook something,"},{"time":1065940,"text":"and they teach three of their mates,"},{"time":1067704,"text":"that only has to repeat itself 25 times,"},{"time":1070052,"text":"and that's the whole\npopulation of America."},{"time":1072331,"text":"Romantic, yes, but most importantly,"},{"time":1076655,"text":"it's about trying to get people to realize"},{"time":1079370,"text":"that every one of your individual efforts\nmakes a difference."},{"time":1082378,"text":"We've got to put back what's been lost."},{"time":1085072,"text":"Huntington's Kitchen."},{"time":1086935,"text":"Huntington, where I made this program,"},{"time":1089230,"text":"we've got this prime-time program"},{"time":1090841,"text":"that hopefully will inspire people\nto really get on this change."},{"time":1094053,"text":"I truly believe that change will happen."},{"time":1096108,"text":"Huntington's Kitchen.\nI work with a community."},{"time":1098299,"text":"I worked in the schools."},{"time":1099804,"text":"I found local sustainable funding"},{"time":1102093,"text":"to get every single school in the area\nfrom the junk, onto the fresh food:"},{"time":1106403,"text":"six-and-a-half grand per school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1108940,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1110170,"text":"That's all it takes,\nsix-and-a-half grand per school."},{"time":1112690,"text":"The Kitchen is 25 grand a month. Okay?"},{"time":1115117,"text":"This can do 5,000 people a year,"},{"time":1118016,"text":"which is 10 percent of their population,"},{"time":1120158,"text":"and it's people on people."},{"time":1121563,"text":"You know, it's local cooks\nteaching local people."},{"time":1123888,"text":"It's free cooking lessons,\nguys, in the Main Street."},{"time":1128280,"text":"This is real, tangible change,\nreal, tangible change."},{"time":1132424,"text":"Around America, if we just look back now,"},{"time":1135470,"text":"there is plenty of wonderful\nthings going on."},{"time":1138574,"text":"There is plenty of beautiful\nthings going on."},{"time":1140707,"text":"There are angels\naround America doing great things"},{"time":1143940,"text":"in schools -- farm-to-school set-ups,"},{"time":1146861,"text":"garden set-ups, education --"},{"time":1149496,"text":"there are amazing people\ndoing this already."},{"time":1151617,"text":"The problem is they all want to roll out"},{"time":1153570,"text":"what they're doing to the next school,"},{"time":1155729,"text":"but there's no cash."},{"time":1157997,"text":"We need to recognize the experts\nand the angels quickly,"},{"time":1161721,"text":"identify them, and allow them\nto easily find the resource"},{"time":1164940,"text":"to keep rolling out\nwhat they're already doing,"},{"time":1167204,"text":"and doing well."},{"time":1168788,"text":"Businesses of America need to support"},{"time":1171084,"text":"Mrs. Obama to do the things\nthat she wants to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1173940,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1180363,"text":"And look, I know it's weird"},{"time":1182333,"text":"having an English person\nstanding here before you"},{"time":1184940,"text":"talking about all this."},{"time":1186405,"text":"All I can say is: I care."},{"time":1188309,"text":"I'm a father,"},{"time":1189755,"text":"and I love this country."},{"time":1191940,"text":"And I believe truly, actually,"},{"time":1194566,"text":"that if change can be made\nin this country,"},{"time":1197439,"text":"beautiful things will happen\naround the world."},{"time":1199646,"text":"If America does it,\nother people will follow."},{"time":1201805,"text":"It's incredibly important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1203577,"text":"(Audience) Yeah!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1204669,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1210324,"text":"When I was in Huntington,"},{"time":1211626,"text":"trying to get a few things to work\nwhen they weren't,"},{"time":1214274,"text":"I thought \"If I had a magic wand,\nwhat would I do?\""},{"time":1219609,"text":"And I thought, \"You know what?"},{"time":1221190,"text":"I'd just love to be put in front\nof some of the most amazing"},{"time":1224497,"text":"movers and shakers in America.\""},{"time":1227181,"text":"And a month later, TED phoned me up\nand gave me this award."},{"time":1231733,"text":"I'm here."},{"time":1235455,"text":"So, my wish."},{"time":1241675,"text":"Dyslexic, so I'm a bit slow."},{"time":1248940,"text":"My wish"},{"time":1250940,"text":"is for you to help a strong,\nsustainable movement"},{"time":1255095,"text":"to educate every child"},{"time":1258793,"text":"about food,"},{"time":1261205,"text":"to inspire families to cook again,"},{"time":1264744,"text":"and to empower people everywhere"},{"time":1267429,"text":"to fight obesity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1269940,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1280183,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1281260,"text":"(Applause continues)"}]}]}